user

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • user.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides an abstract version of a user profile. The profile consists of the users date of birth, name, weight, height, gender. The BMI is estimated by a commonly used formula found on wikipedia. The user profile also has the event container that holds all of the activity events associated with the user.
    Author:
    Fitr.Team
